snippet.textDisplay: Pure Sindhi ensemble: Peacock, Blue Dolphin, traditional folk lore of Umar Marvi, Thar local female singers, Rulli’s multiple usage, Sindhi traditional musical instruments, Mangi’s Rap & Rajper’s beautiful melodious singing! Perfect usage of Sindhi Art from Tharparkar! Seen the same at Makli graveyard! Hats off to the master piece!
